<h4><a href="https://www.axios.com/newsletters/axios-pro-rata">苹果否认对收购 TikTok 感兴趣</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356592" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/TikTok-owner-ByteDance-planning-streaming-music-service.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="512" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/TikTok-owner-ByteDance-planning-streaming-music-service.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/TikTok-owner-ByteDance-planning-streaming-music-service-360x180.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/TikTok-owner-ByteDance-planning-streaming-music-service-768x384.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>多个信源告诉 Axios，苹果对收购 TikTok 表示感兴趣，但强调暂时没有苹果内部信源确认这个消息。随后，苹果发言人告诉 Axios，苹果内部没有讨论收购 TikTok 该事宜，公司也对此不感兴趣。</p>
<p>如果苹果真的收购 TikTok，这将成为其金额最大的一笔收购。目前其最大收购为以 30 亿美元收购 Beats，而《The Information》表示 TikTok 估值可以去到 300 亿美元或更高。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1011221.htm">华为 Mate 40 Pro 渲染图曝光</a></h4>
<p>快科技消息，oneleaks 分享了华为 Mate 40 和 Mate 40 Pro 的渲染图。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356594" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-4.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="400" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-4.jpg 600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-4-360x240.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
<p>从图中可见，Mate 40 采用双曲面挖孔屏，挖孔在左上角。背部是圆形四摄，侧边的实体电源、音量键均得到保留。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356593" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-1.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-1.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-1-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-1-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>Mate 40 Pro 的曲率较高，背部同样采用圆形四摄，其中一颗为方形潜望式变焦镜头，顶部暂不确认是 3.5mm 耳机孔还是红外发射预留。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356595" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pro.jpg" alt="" width="1986" height="977" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pro.jpg 1986w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pro-360x177.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pro-768x378.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pro-1024x504.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1986px) 100vw, 1986px" /></p>
<h4><a href="https://www.theverge.com/2020/8/4/21354593/mulan-release-date-disney-earnings-warner-bros-tenet-theaters">《花木兰》将于 Disney+ 首映</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356596" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1_NFrkkczXC1pKlbLkJ-wgIg.jpeg" alt="" width="2500" height="1547" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1_NFrkkczXC1pKlbLkJ-wgIg.jpeg 2500w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1_NFrkkczXC1pKlbLkJ-wgIg-360x223.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1_NFrkkczXC1pKlbLkJ-wgIg-768x475.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1_NFrkkczXC1pKlbLkJ-wgIg-1024x634.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px" /></p>
<p>The Verge 消息，迪士尼真人电影《花木兰》将于 9 月 4 日在迪士尼流媒体 Disney+ 首映，想观看的订阅用户需额外支付 29.9 美元的费用。官方表示，Disney+ 订阅用户已经超过六千万。</p>
<p>迪士尼 CEO Bob Chapek 补充，在 Disney+ 尚未上线的市场，迪士尼将于同一日期在电影院上映《花木兰》，目前暂无关于中国市场定档相关的确切消息。</p>
<h4><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293888" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji.png" alt="" width="1715" height="300" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji.png 1715w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1715px) 100vw, 1715px" /></h4>
<h4><a href="https://weibo.com/1642720480/Jepmt1f1c?from=page_1002061642720480_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime&amp;type=comment#_rnd1596580981121">苹果更新了 27 英寸 iMac</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356597" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/61e9ece0gy1ghf6teowrfj20zj0tv1fm.jpg" alt="" width="1279" height="1075" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/61e9ece0gy1ghf6teowrfj20zj0tv1fm.jpg 1279w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/61e9ece0gy1ghf6teowrfj20zj0tv1fm-360x303.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/61e9ece0gy1ghf6teowrfj20zj0tv1fm-768x646.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/61e9ece0gy1ghf6teowrfj20zj0tv1fm-1024x861.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1279px) 100vw, 1279px" /></p>
<p>昨晚，苹果在官网上更新了 27 英寸 iMac，起售价为 14399 元。</p>
<p>新 iMac 外观基本没有变化，依然配备了 27 英寸 5K 视网膜显示屏，但提供了 Nano-texture 纳米纹理玻璃面板的选配，全部标配固态硬盘。而处理器方面，则从第八 / 九代英特尔 Core 处理器升级为英特尔第十代 Core 处理器。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.pingwest.com/w/215576">iOS 14 开发者测试版 Beta 4 发布，3D Touch 功能回归</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356621" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/de.png" alt="" width="703" height="683" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/de.png 703w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/de-360x350.png 360w" sizes="(max-width: 703px) 100vw, 703px" /></p>
<p>品玩消息，苹果发布了 iOS 14 和 iPadOS 14 的第四个开发者测试版，在上一个版本中暂时取消的 3D Touch 功能宣布回归。</p>
<p>此外，Beta 4 中加入了曝光通知 API（Exposure Notification API），这主要用于苹果和 Google 合作推出的疫情追踪系统。Beta 4 还对搜索功能进行了改进，并增加了一个新的 Apple TV 小工具。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293889" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://9to5mac.com/2020/08/04/apple-veteran-phil-schiller-transitions-to-new-fellow-role-greg-joswiak-promoted-to-svp-of-marketing/">Phil Schiller 卸任苹果全球营销高级副总裁，Greg Joswiak 接任</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356598" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0-64559-DD246973-2874-4A04-B79F-5C69FA3B8646-xl.jpg" alt="" width="870" height="485" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0-64559-DD246973-2874-4A04-B79F-5C69FA3B8646-xl.jpg 870w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0-64559-DD246973-2874-4A04-B79F-5C69FA3B8646-xl-360x201.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0-64559-DD246973-2874-4A04-B79F-5C69FA3B8646-xl-768x428.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 870px) 100vw, 870px" /></p>
<p>9to5mac 消息，Phil Schiller 将转为担任「Apple Fellow」，Greg Joswiak 接任其苹果全球营销高级副总裁一职。</p>
<p>作为「Apple Fellow」，Schiller 将「领导 App Store 和苹果活动」，通过合作伙伴关系为苹果服务，并直接向苹果 CEO 库克汇报。</p>
<h4><a href="https://new.qq.com/omn/TEC20200/TEC2020080200427500.html">软银计划继续持有芯片设计公司 ARM 股份</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356599" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/38-1-KCIKH.jpg" alt="" width="1300" height="729" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/38-1-KCIKH.jpg 1300w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/38-1-KCIKH-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/38-1-KCIKH-768x431.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/38-1-KCIKH-1024x574.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1300px) 100vw, 1300px" /></p>
<p>腾讯科技消息，知情人士透露，软银计划继续维持其所持 ARM 股份，即使它将部分股权出售给英伟达或进行 IPO。</p>
<p>一位知情人士称「ARM 进行 IPO 的计划没有改变」，但软银并未排除达成双边交易的可能性，目前正在权衡这两个选项。一种可能性是英伟达收购 ARM 后软银入股这家芯片巨头。另一种情况是英伟达和 ARM 通过换股合并，软银成为合并后公司的大股东。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1011569.htm">IDC：190g 以下的 5G 手机占比近 50%</a></h4>
<p>快科技消息，IDC 报告显示，截至 6 月，国内已有近 50% 的 5G 手机是 190g 以下的轻薄手机。在初期，5G 手机大部分机身都超过 190g，200g 以上的产品也一度超过 30% 的占比。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356600" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/23296819bf9ce9b.png" alt="" width="600" height="469" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/23296819bf9ce9b.png 600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/23296819bf9ce9b-360x281.png 360w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
<p>IDC 认为，未来，轻薄手机将会始终在市场中占据重要位置。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.cls.cn/detail/550031">马斯克承认 Cybertruck 可能「彻底失败」</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356601" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/https___cdn.cnn_.com_cnnnext_dam_assets_191122092415-01-tesla-cybertruck-musk-1121.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/https___cdn.cnn_.com_cnnnext_dam_assets_191122092415-01-tesla-cybertruck-musk-1121.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/https___cdn.cnn_.com_cnnnext_dam_assets_191122092415-01-tesla-cybertruck-musk-1121-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/https___cdn.cnn_.com_cnnnext_dam_assets_191122092415-01-tesla-cybertruck-musk-1121-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/https___cdn.cnn_.com_cnnnext_dam_assets_191122092415-01-tesla-cybertruck-musk-1121-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>财联社消息，特斯拉 CEO 马斯克在接受媒体采访时表示，如果 Cybertruck 失败，更传统的皮卡是「备用策略」。</p>
<p>马斯克表示，特斯拉并未对这款卡车的科幻设计进行任何消费者研究，甚至可以说是完全没有考虑市场对于这款皮卡的接受度。如果人们不愿意接受它，马斯克会对外观更传统的特斯拉卡车持开放态度。</p>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/8/adidas-originals-human-made-spring-summer-2020-collection-info">adidas Originals 推出和 HUMAN MADE 合作的新联名系列</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356602" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/12.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/12.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/12-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/12-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/12-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>Hypebeast 消息，adidas Originals 和 HUMAN MADE 再次合作，基于 Stan Smith、Campus 和 Rivalry 三个经典鞋款推出了一系列新的联名款。该系列将于 8 月 6 日发售。</p>
